\series bold
connecting vector
\begin_inset LatexCommand \index{connectig vector}

\end_inset


\series default
 for the vector field 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}$
\end_inset

 if 
\begin_inset Formula $\left[\mathbf{c},\mathbf{v}\right]=0$
\end_inset

.
 (Since 
\begin_inset Formula $[\mathbf{c},\mathbf{v}]=-[\mathbf{v},\mathbf{c}]$
\end_inset

