\series bold
spherical coordinates 
\series default

\begin_inset LatexCommand \index{spherical coordinates}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \theta,\phi\right\} $
\end_inset

, defined by
\begin_inset Formula \[
x=r\cos\theta\cos\phi,\; y=r\cos\theta\sin\phi,\; z=r\sin\theta,\]

\end_inset

do not constitute a global coordinate system on 
\begin_inset Formula $S^{2}$
\end_inset

