\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If 
\begin_inset Formula $\eta_{ab}$
\end_inset

 is the canonical form of the metric, the divergence of a vector field 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{u}$
\end_inset

 is
\begin_inset Formula \[
\textrm{div}\mathbf{u}=\left(\det\eta_{ab}\right)*\textrm{d}*\hat{g}\mathbf{u}.\]

\end_inset

 
\end_layout

