\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 within proper time 
\begin_inset Formula $3/\theta_{0}$
\end_inset

 from 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Under the conditions of Statement\InsetSpace ~
3, the geodesic 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

 normal to 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

