\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

corner
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 so the tangent 3-space to 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{H}$
\end_inset

 is undefined.
 A null surface locally separates a past subdomain from a future subdomain,
