\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

, and consider the causal structure of the tangent space at 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

.
 We are assuming that 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 is not a singularity, so that 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

 can be continued past 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

.
