\begin_inset Formula \[
L(q,\dot{q})=\frac{1}{2}m\dot{q}^{2}-V(q),\]

\end_inset

describing a particle of mass 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 in a potential 
\begin_inset Formula $V(q)$
\end_inset

.
