\begin_inset Formula \[
\tilde{L}(q,\dot{q},\ddot{q})=-\frac{1}{2}mq\ddot{q}-V(q).\]

\end_inset

However, the Lagrangian 
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{L}$
\end_inset

