\end_inset

The variation of the boundary term is 
\begin_inset Formula \[
\delta\left.\frac{1}{2}mq\dot{q}\right|_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}=\left.\frac{1}{2}mq\delta\dot{q}\right|_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}+\left.\frac{1}{2}m\dot{q}\delta q\right|_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}},\]

\end_inset

which precisely cancels the unwanted term with 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\dot{q}$
\end_inset

 in the variation 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\tilde{L}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

