\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-dimensional space, it remains to prove that the proportionality factor
 
\begin_inset Formula $\det\hat{T}$
\end_inset

 is actually independent of the choice of the vectors 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \mathbf{v}_{j}\right\} $
\end_inset

.
 (It will follow that 
\begin_inset Formula $\det\hat{T}$
\end_inset

 coincides with the determinant defined through an orthogonal basis.)
