\end_inset

 into 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{u}_{1}\wedge...\wedge\mathbf{u}_{n}$
\end_inset

.
 Therefore the desired relationship for 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \mathbf{u}_{j}\right\} $
\end_inset

 follows.
