-form
\begin_inset Formula \[
\omega_{1}\wedge*\omega_{2}=\sum_{k_{1},...,k_{n}}\frac{\eta^{k_{1}k_{1}}...\eta^{k_{n}k_{n}}}{n!}\left(\iota_{\mathbf{e}_{k_{n}}}...\iota_{\mathbf{e}_{k_{1}}}\omega_{2}\right)\omega_{1}\wedge\left(\iota_{\mathbf{e}_{k_{n}}}...\iota_{\mathbf{e}_{k_{1}}}\boldsymbol{\varepsilon}\right);\]

