\begin_inset Formula $\omega_{1}\leftrightarrow\omega_{2}$
\end_inset

.
 We use Eq.\InsetSpace ~
(
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{eq:Hodge star of N-form}

\end_inset

) to compute the Hodge dual of this 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

-form,
\begin_inset Formula \[
