\end_inset

In the expression\InsetSpace ~
(
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{eq:wedge permutation 1}

\end_inset

), the summation is performed over all permutations 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

 of the set 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ 1,...,N\right\} $
\end_inset

.
