\begin_inset Formula \[
\boldsymbol{\varepsilon}(\mathbf{e}_{k_{1}},...,\mathbf{e}_{k_{n}},\mathbf{e}_{\sigma(n+1)},...,\mathbf{e}_{\sigma(N)})=0\]

\end_inset

unless the set 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ k_{1},...,k_{n},\sigma(n+1),...,\sigma(N)\right\} $
\end_inset

